	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Not talking about PCB design, but rather tracing out scans of existing boards. Anyone know if such software is out there?
<br />
<br />Basically hoping to find something where I can give it high-res scans of both sides of an unpopulated PCB and then it can show you the complete path of any given trace, including ones that go back and forth between sides.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


