	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It probably won't be automatic. First, one would have to use GIMP to reduce each of the PCB's layers (two in this case) to monochrome so that flood fills can work. But even so, I'll guess it'd still be less error-prone than manual tracing.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
